desc_short	-----								Music. Lasers. Space. Plasma. Rockets. Bosses. Serene and peaceful space scenery, just to contrast this all. Melt your eyes off your face in Polynomial 2. Or melt your Virtual Reality headset onto your face. Supports normal displays, HTC Vive, and Oculus Rift VR headsets.							
